{"tid":551860,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「沈判日」係畜牲講嘅說話！","createTime":"2018-02-06T04:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T04:37:50.000Z","uid":19322,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d7440f0382046a4cbb8329d44e8aa1e2660eb93","tid":551860,"uid":19322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"人稱「沈大師」的訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈一直睇淡後市，果然，港股今日出現「沈判日」，大市暴瀉。<br />\n<br />\n正當戰友欲哭無淚，牛仔屍橫遍野之際，網絡流傳一段沈大師錄音：<br />\n<br />\n「有時我真係唔想講唔得嘅，（啲人）成日話畀你聽，揸住錢冇用呀，揸住錢係一世捱窮，一世揸兜呀，冇發達呀，揸住現金一世揸兜呀。呢啲唔係人講嘅說話，係畜牲講嘅說話！你根本就推緊人去死！你炒得叻又如何，你肯定你唔會輸？呢啲咁嘅說話，你會害咗好多人，所以我一定要堅持，叫人唔好入市！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/06/122747_5ddd71835e9e1e2d37c2a927dfd34fe6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F06%2F122747_5ddd71835e9e1e2d37c2a927dfd34fe6.png&h=d3858fc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"764dc885ce92e15b4bd87d93afd74c510cc734b1","tid":551860,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"即刻出黎抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92954c8a58f367fe739fbcf393fcb5d1b5a0684d","tid":551860,"uid":109386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T04:29:11.000Z","msg":"知錯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5bb4102be8620bfed5fe3d25af64c90beeae276","tid":551860,"uid":19322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"沈大師我知錯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb37d84eb7f49454888141a1adaa73463bf1747","tid":551860,"uid":5278,"